title: Takar Paja
text: Takar Paja (born 18 January 1994) is an Indian <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He made his <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> debut for <a href="Arunachal%20Pradesh%20cricket%20team">Arunachal Pradesh</a> in the <a href="2018%E2%80%9319%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy">2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy</a> on 28 September 2018.
